      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;hi-im-william&#34;&gt;Hi! I&amp;rsquo;m William&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ever since starting my job at a certain government agency, I&amp;rsquo;ve thought a lot more about accessibility.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;And as you&amp;rsquo;ll find out, I like getting things on paper—whether metaphorically or not.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I like to get things on paper (both literally and metaphorically). That&amp;rsquo;s why I funded my own placement in the University of Sunshine Coast &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.unisc.edu.au/study/courses-and-programs/short-courses-and-microcredentials/inclusive-digital-design-for-business&#34;&gt;Inclusive Digital Design for Business&lt;/a&gt; course. I have yet to pass the course, so wish me luck.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
